    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom shine and absolutely no scratches or dings, while the interior remains pristine with that new-car smell and no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a complete service history. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a vehicle in peak collector-grade condition.",
      "price": 48000.0,
